Class ManualLocationHandler.downloadGeocode

    private static class ManualLocationHandler.downloadGeocode

    A private class that is instantiated in geocode, and it is used to download a call to the Open Mapquest Nominatim search. It'll try and convert a location to their geo-coordinates. Calls downloadFromURL to try and download and return that data.
